# ─── deploy/k8s/secrets/.gitignore ───────────────────────────────────────────
#
# This directory is a safe scratchpad for intermediate per-key sealed outputs.
# Run: ./scripts/seal_secret.sh seal KEY VALUE SECRET_NAME KEY_NAME
# to seal a single value and print it; redirect to a file here if needed.
#
# ALL FILES in this directory are gitignored to prevent accidental secret leaks.
# The directory itself is tracked so teammates can use it as a working area.
#
# To seal all secrets at once: ./scripts/seal_secret.sh seal-all
# That writes directly to: deploy/k8s/base/sealed-secret-apex.yaml (safe to commit)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Ignore everything in this directory except this .gitignore
*
!.gitignore
